# _ldc2-cli — LDC Team ldc2-cli CLI command-line frontend wrapping the LDC LLVM-based D compiler that uses the official DMD frontend to support the latest version of D2 with the powerful LLVM backend open-source written in D and C++ originally Tomas Lindquist Olsen now LDC Team David Nadlinger Martin Kinkelin LLVM-backend D2 ldmd2 cross-compile WebAssembly bitcode iOS Android ARM RISC-V WASI LDC.intrinsics inline-asm linker-flags release debug O0 O1 O2 O3 Os mtriple mtarget mcpu mattr ffast-math ofile od of v vcolumns vasm vcg-ast verror-style verbose-cg link-defaultlib-shared link-internally lto LTO unittest betterC fuse-ld coverage profile-instr-generate (LDC Team Tomas Lindquist Olsen David Nadlinger Martin Kinkelin, D/C++); custom argparse
# upstream: https://github.com/ldc-developers/ldc

